@{
	ViewBag.Title = "Contribute";
}
<div class="box box-default">
	<div class="box-header with-border">
		<h3 class="box-title">@ViewBag.Title</h3>
		<div class="box-tools pull-right">
			<button class="btn btn-box-tool" data-widget="collapse"><i class="fa fa-minus"></i></button>
		</div><!-- /.box-tools -->
	</div><!-- /.box-header -->
	<div class="box-body">
		<p>
			This website is made by enthusiastic programmers who have a love for having fun in games!
		</p>
		<p>
			Everything you see here is made in their spare time and we appreciate every suggestion you send to us!
		</p>
		<p>
			<strong>Why would you contribute? It works right?</strong><br />
			Well, let me be honest running this website isn't cheap, we pay a yearly fee for the domains, approximatly 20 euro's.<br />
			We pay a monthly fee for hosting/connection/database and traffic, which costs us 20-30 euro's a month.<br />
			It would be a great help and a fantastic gesture if you donated a bit of money, every amount helps!<br />
			You could also add a little message or request with your donation!
		</p>

		<p>Everyway of supporting is very much appreciated! You can help us by:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				Donating <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">
					<input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
					<input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="LYTU3CTS4AEAL">
					<input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_GB/i/btn/btn_donate_SM.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal – The safer, easier way to pay online.">
					<img alt="" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/nl_NL/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">
				</form>
			</li>
			<li>Helping build on the Open Source project <a href="https://github.com/jeanpoelie/StratRoulette-C-">Github </a></li>
			<li>Filling our database with strat ideas, please send them to <a href="mailto:stratgameroulette@gmail.com">Strat Roulette</a></li>
			<li>Give in a bit of your spare time to help us out with one of the chores below!</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>	  

<div class="box box-default">
	<div class="box-header with-border">
		<h3 class="box-title">Promoting</h3>
		<div class="box-tools pull-right">
			<button class="btn btn-box-tool" data-widget="collapse"><i class="fa fa-minus"></i></button>
		</div><!-- /.box-tools -->
	</div><!-- /.box-header -->
	<div class="box-body">
		<p>Tell your friends/collegues or the people who you play games with, or meet, about us! This helps out a lot (We do not earn any money for visits/or adverts since we don't have any, but support always motivates)!</p>
	</div><!-- /.box-body -->
</div><!-- /.box -->

<div class="box box-default">
	<div class="box-header with-border">
		<h3 class="box-title">Share</h3>
		<div class="box-tools pull-right">
			<button class="btn btn-box-tool" data-widget="collapse"><i class="fa fa-minus"></i></button>
		</div><!-- /.box-tools -->
	</div><!-- /.box-header -->
	<div class="box-body">
		<p>Share your idea's/thoughts with us so that we can grow into a bigger community and a better website! When you are interested contact us thru the @Html.ActionLink("Contact Page", "Contact").</p>
	</div><!-- /.box-body -->
</div><!-- /.box -->	


<div class="box box-default">
	<div class="box-header with-border">
		<h3 class="box-title">Design/Program</h3>
		<div class="box-tools pull-right">
			<button class="btn btn-box-tool" data-widget="collapse"><i class="fa fa-minus"></i></button>
		</div><!-- /.box-tools -->
	</div><!-- /.box-header -->
	<div class="box-body">
		<p>If you are a designer or a programmer you can help us out by drawing images for the website or program for us! When you are interested contact us thru the @Html.ActionLink("Contact Page", "Contact").</p>
	</div><!-- /.box-body -->
</div><!-- /.box -->